<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Password Reset</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;'
  >
    <table
      width='100%'
      cellpadding='0'
      cellspacing='0'
      style='background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px;'
    >
      <tr>
        <td>
          <h1 style='color: #4A90E2; text-align: center;'>Group Request</h1>
          <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
          <p>We received a request to join a farm group. If you didn't make
            this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
          <p>To accept request, click the button below:</p>
          <table width='100%' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0'>
            <tr>
              <td align='center'>
                <a
                  href='{{requestLink}}'
                  style='display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #4A90E2; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;'
                >Accept Request</a>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
          <p style='word-break: break-all;'><a
              href='{{requestLink}}'
              style='color: #4A90E2;'
            >{{resetLink}}</a></p>
          <p>This request link will expire in 24 hours for security
            reasons.</p>
          <p>If you didn't request to join any group, please contact our support
            team immediately.</p>
          <p>Best regards,<br />Your Application Team</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <p
      style='text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #888888; margin-top: 20px;'
    >
      This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
